{"275352":{"detail":{"date":"2019-07-04","platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/97/29/275352_KlYI2.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/97/29/275352_KlYI2.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/97/29/275352_KlYI2.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/97/29/275352_KlYI2.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/97/29/275352_KlYI2.jpg"},"summary":"年纪轻轻便崭露头角成为远近闻名的青年冒险者“戴尔”，由于某次委托而步入了幽深的森林中的他，与骨瘦如柴的年幼的魔族少女“拉提娜”相遇了。\r\n戴尔无法对背负着罪人烙印的拉提娜置之不理，并下定决心要成为她的监护人——\r\n“拉提娜太可爱了，我不想去工作。”\r\n——戴尔不知不觉就变为笨蛋父亲模式全开！？","name":"うちの娘の為ならば、俺はもしかしたら魔王も倒せるかもしれない。","name_cn":"为了女儿，我说不定连魔王都能干掉。","tags":[{"name":"萝莉","count":485,"total_cont":0},{"name":"异世界","count":450,"total_cont":0},{"name":"轻小说改","count":436,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2019年7月","count":418,"total_cont":0},{"name":"治愈","count":348,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":276,"total_cont":0},{"name":"奇幻","count":229,"total_cont":0},{"name":"MAHOFILM","count":157,"total_cont":0},{"name":"恋爱","count":156,"total_cont":0},{"name":"轻改","count":150,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2019","count":128,"total_cont":0},{"name":"萌","count":122,"total_cont":0},{"name":"养女儿","count":63,"total_cont":0},{"name":"小说改","count":54,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":43,"total_cont":0},{"name":"MAHO_FILM","count":26,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日常","count":17,"total_cont":0},{"name":"柳瀬雄之","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"女儿","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本动画","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"父嫁","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2019年","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"柳濑雄之","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"萌系","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"季番","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"高尾奏音","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"冒险","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"战斗","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"魔法","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"吉岡たかを","count":3,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"为了女儿，我说不定连魔王都能干掉。"},{"key":"话数","value":"12"},{"key":"放送开始","valu