,"platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/54/bb/275371_naGaN.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/54/bb/275371_naGaN.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/54/bb/275371_naGaN.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/54/bb/275371_naGaN.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/54/bb/275371_naGaN.jpg"},"summary":"没有女朋友的履历=年龄的普通高中生桐生慧辉，突然收到一封情书。\r\n他因为终于能交到女朋友而感到欢喜，但情书上却没有寄信人的名字，而且不知为何里面还附带一条纯白胖次……???\r\n他周围的那些可爱女孩们每个都很可疑，而且似乎都各有内情的样子\r\n究竟“掉了胖次的灰姑娘”会是谁呢？\r\n谜团接连浮现，甚至将变态招至身旁的新感觉变态涌现系恋爱喜剧开始……!!","name":"可愛ければ変態でも好きになってくれますか？","name_cn":"只要可爱即使是变态你也会喜欢我吧？","tags":[{"name":"后宫","count":1258,"total_cont":0},{"name":"恋爱","count":1091,"total_cont":0},{"name":"校园","count":780,"total_cont":0},{"name":"搞笑","count":740,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2019年7月","count":729,"total_cont":0},{"name":"轻小说改","count":709,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":491,"total_cont":0},{"name":"GeekToys","count":378,"total_cont":0},{"name":"变态","count":358,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2019","count":342,"total_cont":0},{"name":"卖肉","count":316,"total_cont":0},{"name":"轻改","count":294,"total_cont":0},{"name":"只要可爱即使是变态你也会喜欢我吧？","count":126,"total_cont":0},{"name":"小说改","count":98,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":60,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日常","count":31,"total_cont":0},{"name":"妹控","count":20,"total_cont":0},{"name":"肉","count":14,"total_cont":0},{"name":"伊魔崎斋","count":13,"total_cont":0},{"name":"いまざきいつき","count":12,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"肉番","count":9,"total_cont":0},{"name":"竹达彩奈","count":9,"total_cont":0},{"name":"喜剧","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"兄妹","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"党争","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本动画","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2019夏","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2019年","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"山下宪一","count":5,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"只要可爱即使是变态你也会喜欢我吧？"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"v":"只要长得可爱，即使是变态你也喜欢吗？"}]}